                    <div style="font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Arial,sans-serif;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px;">Competition Report</div>
